you don't want the answers to.

376
00:15:18,931 --> 00:15:20,815
I'm sorry
you feel that way,

377
00:15:20,882 --> 00:15:22,850
but if you can't handle me
seeing other firms,

378
00:15:22,918 --> 00:15:25,319
then maybe you're not the man
that I thought you were,

379
00:15:25,370 --> 00:15:28,439
and maybe you don't deserve
Brian Galloway.

380
00:15:28,524 --> 00:15:29,907
Deserve him?

381
00:15:29,992 --> 00:15:31,358
You don't get to make
that determination.

382
00:15:31,410 --> 00:15:34,262
Yes, I do.
I'm Sheila Amanda Sazs,

383
00:15:34,329 --> 00:15:36,531
and if I say
you don't deserve him,

384
00:15:36,598 --> 00:15:39,200
you don't get to have him.
I don't care who you are.

385
00:15:39,268 --> 00:15:40,768
If I want him,
I can have him,

386
00:15:40,819 --> 00:15:42,069
and I'm going to take him
six ways from Sunday

387
00:15:42,121 --> 00:15:43,271
and there's nothing you can do
to stop me.

