389
00:15:44,573 --> 00:15:46,240
because when I'm done
talking to him,

390
00:15:46,308 --> 00:15:48,943
there's no way on earth he'll
end up at Pearson Darby Specter

391
00:15:49,011 --> 00:15:50,111
