without saying a word.

397
00:16:08,897 --> 00:16:10,932
What did you expect,
a fruit basket

398
00:16:10,999 --> 00:16:13,301
for getting me out of a crime
your firm committed?

399
00:16:13,368 --> 00:16:15,169
Ava, I know Travis Tanner
fed you a line

400
