didn't feed me anything.

402
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:21,242
This is the result
of your actions.

403
00:16:21,310 --> 00:16:23,494
Wait a second,
you really did go to him?

404
00:16:23,579 --> 00:16:26,581
I looked into you
when I was deciding to hire you.

405
00:16:26,648 --> 00:16:28,149
You think I wouldn't do
the same thing again

406
00:16:28,217 --> 00:16:29,884
when I decided
to come after you?

407
00:16:29,952 --> 00:16:31,452
When you looked into me,

408
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:32,820
you found out
that whatever I do

409
00:16:32,871 --> 00:16:35,356
