I ever did for you.

410
00:16:35,424 --> 00:16:36,991
What you did
was intimidate people

411
00:16:37,059 --> 00:16:39,227
and what it did
was backfire onto me.

412
00:16:39,294 --> 00:16:42,296
Well, now I've found someone
you can't intimidate,

413
00:16:42,364 --> 00:16:44,265
and it's backfiring
onto you.

414
00:16:44,332 --> 00:16:45,967
Now, if you'll excuse me,

415
00:16:46,034 --> 00:16:47,335
